snippet.title: NoPixel Live
snippet.description:
Welcome to your new HUB for all things NoPixel!

This channel aims to provide quality, up to date content from a variety of streamers that RP on the
NoPixel server. 99% of our content will be in server, however you will find one offs of IRL streams, reactions and more if you look hard enough (Mostly about Burn).
We take requests in the community tab via poll to feature your favorite characters and have a big focus on community driven content if the opportunity presents itself. 
Come join us and get involved!

(All times CST)
Video release schedule: 
Mon-Friday : 1 p.m. - 1 a.m.
Saturday/Sunday : 5 p.m. - 12 a.m.
-Any days off will be announced in the community tab-

~Times may vary slightly, but you can usually expect videos by 5 if not on schedule! ~


To contact us about opportunities, taking down a video or anything business related, 
you can reach us at : 
nopixellive@gmail.com
! No soliciting please !
